{"tid":1435135,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"方仲賢發燒取消記者會","createTime":"2019-08-09T03:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:02:44.000Z","uid":41343,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0ecdd41168cb1ea093cfe59d95b22bc27c54419b","tid":1435135,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:17:10.000Z","msg":"在深水埗買「觀星筆」被捕的浸大學生會長方仲賢，昨晚獲警方無條件釋放後，原定今午在浸大校園召開記者會，回應被捕事件。然而，浸大學生會表示，方仲賢至今仍然發高燒，因此取消今日的記者會。<br />\n<br />\n事緣方仲賢周二晚在深水埗被5名休班警員截查，指他藏有「鐳射槍」，以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器拘捕他，惹起公憤，不少市民質疑警方製造「白色恐怖」，要求放人。至昨晚，警方無條件釋放方仲賢，但保留追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%96%B9%E4%BB%B2%E8%B3%A2%E7%99%BC%E7%87%92%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83-184124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%2587%2592%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%259C%2583-184124&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzSgGTjEty4RfxMaQWzCDCUQ%3D&h=78383457\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%96%B9%E4%BB%B2%E8%B3%A2%E7%99%BC%E7%87%92%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83-184124</a>"},{"pid":"f71280df78c8778260825977d4433c93a19667a8","tid":1435135,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63122333472cd0cf6ed8957e961c90c5489cbd8","tid":1435135,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:21:06.000Z","msg":"頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738a8ca3637c547d2ebff056efdd1294e607d6c8","tid":1435135,"uid":83348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":